+**Constitutional Authority**: Principles I-XIV (All Principles)
+**Source Documents**:
+- CLAUDE.md "Commands" and "Key Architecture" sections
+- `.specify/scripts/bash/` workflow scripts
+- `.specify/memory/constitution.md`
